 lattice is impossible even for a\nlattice without any defects if $k\\gtrapprox 6 \\times 10^3$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Dec 2014 06:48:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-16"}
